4.2.3　モデル選択における目的関数の準備¶

5mean accuracy scoreC, gamma

In [5]:
def objective(trial):
    # 
    C = trial.suggest_loguniform("C", 1e-02, 1e+02)
    gamma = trial.suggest_loguniform("gamma", 1e-02, 1e+02)
    
    # 
    svc = SVC(C = C, gamma = gamma, kernel = "rbf")
    
    # 5
    # X = X_train, y = y_train
    result = cross_validate(estimator = svc, X = X_train, y = y_train, 
                            cv = kf, scoring = "accuracy")
    val_accuracy = result["test_score"].mean()
    
    return val_accuracy

4.2.4　optunaによる最適化¶

optuna2

  2. optimize
In [6]:
optuna.logging.set_verbosity(optuna.logging.WARNING)    # optunalog
study = optuna.create_study(direction = "maximize")
study.optimize(objective, n_trials = 100)
study.best_params, study.best_value
Out[6]:
({'C': 0.4847730423131618, 'gamma': 1.3000841999289656}, 0.9122222222222224)

木構造的Parzen推定量¶

$p(m\mid h)$ ParzenTPE Parzen $p(m\mid h)$ $p(h\mid m)$ $m$ $m$ TPE

\begin{eqnarray*} p(h\mid m) &=& \begin{cases}l(h)\text{ if }y>m^*\\ g(h)\text{ if }y\leq m^* \end{cases} \end{eqnarray*}

$l(h)$, $g(h)$

$l(h)$, $g(h)$ : $m_{t}(h)$ $m^{*}$resp. $h$ $m^{*}$resp. $h^{l}_{1},\cdots,h^{l}_{n}$

\begin{align*} \sigma_{i,m} &= \begin{cases} h_{1} - h_{min}\\ \max(h_{i+1}-h_{i}, h_{i}-h_{i-1})\\ h_{max} - h_{\gamma} \end{cases} \end{align*}

Expected Improvement : ParzenExpected Improvement

\begin{eqnarray*} EI_{m^*}(h) &=& \int_{-\infty}^{\infty}\max(m-m^*,0)p(m\mid h)dm\\ &=& \int_{-\infty}^{\infty}\max(m-m^*,0)\frac{p(h\mid m)p(m)}{p(h)}dm\\ &=& \frac{l(h)}{\gamma l(h)+(1-\gamma)g(h)}\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}\max(m-m^*, 0)p(m)dm\\ &\propto& \frac{1}{\gamma+(1-\gamma)\frac{g(h)}{l(h)}} \end{eqnarray*}

$p(x)=\gamma l(h)+(1-\gamma)g(h)$expected improvement $EI_{m^{*}}(h)$ $h$ $g(h)/l(h)$
